Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:57.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:07.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:14.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}狂った時計　刻む命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:18.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}こぼれてく記憶の砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:22.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}芽生えた想いまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:27.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}ねえ　こんなに呆気なく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:34.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:35.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}I wish I was there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:38.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:44.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}二度となにも失くさぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:51.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}私を忘れて　始めて　Restart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:53.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:55.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:24:00.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:05.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.75,0:24:09.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:12.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:14.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:16.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:20.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.52,0:24:22.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:23.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}君と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:57.06,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.31,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你的触碰  我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.82,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}不  请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:07.19,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}尽管这绝望  不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:14.74,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}失准的时钟  记录着生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:18.54,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}散落满地的记忆之砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:22.50,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}以及萌生的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:27.46,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你看  却是那么轻易
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:34.76,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}消失殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:35.85,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}我希望能与你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:38.06,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.06,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你的触碰  我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:44.44,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}为了不再失去曾经拥有的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:51.45,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}让我忘却自己的过去  重新开始旅途
