Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:55.58,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}尽管这绝望  不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:24:00.21,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}愿那让你苦不堪言的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:05.54,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}会迎来完结的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.75,0:24:09.34,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}而我却要目送你离开
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:12.63,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:14.76,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:16.64,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}再一次的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:20.48,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.52,0:24:22.56,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:23.85,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}与你携手迈进
